    "In our case, after extensive discussions in multiple meetings, we were able to complete DCT specifications that reflect our thinking about this theory (see Peters et al., 2020, which also visualizes the relationship between constructs, and see osf.io/me3h2 for all files with DCT specifications and the used R scripts)."
  ]
}